      ******************************************************************
      * TABELAS
      ******************************************************************
      * TABELA PSHEADER  (REG HEADER)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDHEAD6  END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSCONTRAT (CONTRATOS)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDCONTR4 END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSDETALHE (REG DETALHE)
JF0618     EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDDET003 END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSFICHEIR (REG FICHEIRO)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDFICHEI END-EXEC.
